General.Name: TF Bank AB
General.Description: TF Bank AB (publ) provides consumer banking services and e-commerce solutions through a proprietary IT platform. The company operates through three segments: Consumer Lending, Ecommerce Solutions, and Credit Cards. It offers savings accounts; unsecured consumer loans; and digital payment solutions, as well as credit cards. The company serves private individuals in Sweden, Spain, Finland, Norway, Denmark, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Poland, Germany, and Austria. TF Bank AB (publ) was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Borås, Sweden.
